   <h1>Spirited Recipes For Your Father&#8217;s Day Celebration</h1>
	  <ul class="hmenu article-meta">
	    
	    
	  	<li class="first"><a href="http://www.mint.com/blog/author/frugal-foodie/" title="Posts by Frugal Foodie">Frugal Foodie</a> on 6/16/2010</li>
